Nemesis Enforcer:

Nemesis Enforcer looked to Zardus, nodding.  Jumping into the air, he 
trnasformed into his black giant bat mode.  Flapping his wings, he activated 
the rocket boosters in the soles of his feet.  Getting a presice fix on the 
Alliance base, he sent a full gust of power to the boosters, flames sending 
him rocketing off towards the Alliance base as ordered by his leader.
